OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry but
OL,6,Fsomewhat overcast in the evening. Then
OL,7,Fthe rest of the night will be dry with
OL,8,Fvariable amounts of cloud. Freshening
OL,9,Fsoutheasterly winds, becoming strong
OL,10,Facross Shetland later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FDry and bright morning with
OL,13,Fsome sunny spells. Cloudier in the
OL,14,Fafternoon with rain spreading
OL,15,Fnortheast in the evening. Strong
OL,16,Fsoutheasterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
